OL,3,CMan appears in court charged with
OL,4,Cmurder of 'cherished daughter' in
OL,5,CCardiff
OL,7,FA man has appeared in court charged
OL,8,Fwith murder after a 32-year-old woman
OL,9,Fwho was found dead on a Cardiff street
OL,10,Flast week.
OL,12,FThisara Weragalage, 37, of Pentwyn,
OL,13,Fhas been charged with the murder of 32-
OL,14,Fyear-old Niwunhellage Dona Nirodha
OL,15,FKalapni Niwunhella, who was known as
OL,16,FNirodha.
OL,18,FPolice were called to South Morgan
OL,19,FPlace in Riverside just after 7.30am
OL,20,Fon 21 August, where Nirodha died at
OL,21,Fthe scene.
