OL,5,CCardiff
OL,7,FWeragalage appeared at Cardiff Crown
OL,8,FCourt on Tuesday, 26 August, and was
OL,9,Fremanded in custody until a plea
OL,10,Fhearing on 19 September.
OL,12,FA trial date has been set for 9
OL,13,FFebruary, 2026.
OL,15,FIn a tribute, her family said: "We
OL,16,Fremember Nirodha as a cherished
OL,17,Fdaughter, family member and dear
OL,18,Ffriend to many. Nirodha will be
OL,19,Fforever remembered with peace, love
OL,20,Fand gratitude.
